01:49:53,333 --> 01:49:54,875
What did you see?

1758
01:49:56,083 --> 01:49:57,417
The red devil head.

1759
01:49:57,500 --> 01:50:00,708
<i>Blood you assumed was Wicks'.</i>

1760
01:50:00,791 --> 01:50:03,181
Now, I showed you
the answer to this, did you see?

1761
01:50:04,375 --> 01:50:05,583
Il Diavolo.

1762
01:50:05,666 --> 01:50:07,333
The pizza bar. The photograph.

1763
01:50:08,666 --> 01:50:10,666
<i>You thought you saw,</i>

