1775
01:50:37,000 --> 01:50:38,833
The same exact red

1776
01:50:38,916 --> 01:50:42,083
as the mysterious thread
found in the closet.

1777
01:50:42,791 --> 01:50:46,500
<i>Because the second devil head
was there all the time.</i>

1778
01:50:46,583 --> 01:50:48,917
<i>Sewn to the back of his vestments.</i>

1779
01:50:49,000 --> 01:50:50,292
Hollow, light,

1780
