rose from the dead?

1850
01:55:12,416 --> 01:55:13,833
That it was a miracle?

1851
01:55:13,916 --> 01:55:18,042
I'm saying I cannot solve this case.

1852
01:55:19,583 --> 01:55:20,750
That works.

1853
01:55:21,250 --> 01:55:22,083
Thank you.

1854
01:55:24,458 --> 01:55:25,541
Blanc?

