1862
01:55:48,583 --> 01:55:51,458
And would you consider blurbing my book?

1863
01:55:51,541 --> 01:55:53,333
No.

1864
01:55:53,958 --> 01:55:56,592
Okay. All right.
Show's over. Everyone out.

1865
01:55:57,333 --> 01:55:59,750
Out. Out.

1866
01:56:00,458 --> 01:56:02,083
Yeah, can you stand back, sir?

1867
01:56:03,375 --> 01:56:05,000
Okay, can we keep them back...

1868
01:56:06,666 --> 01:56:09,500
I add another chapter
and then we're... we're ready.

1869
01:56:09,583 --> 01:56:11,917
We're ready to publish. Trust me, Alan.

1870
01:56:12,000 --> 01:56:14,708
Call Random House, everybody.
