1899
01:57:50,416 --> 01:57:51,708
Thank you.

1900
01:57:55,583 --> 01:57:57,000
Father Jud.

1901
01:58:04,000 --> 01:58:05,042
What do I do?

1902
01:58:05,125 --> 01:58:06,958
What you were born to do.

1903
01:58:07,041 --> 01:58:08,541
Be her priest.

1904
01:58:09,041 --> 01:58:10,458
Take her confession.

1905
01:58:19,125 --> 01:58:21,042
Bless me, Father, for I have sinned.

